<h4><span id=3D"SEGGER_RTT_ConfigDownBuffer.28.29"></span><span class=3D"mw=
-headline" id=3D"SEGGER_RTT_ConfigDownBuffer()">SEGGER_RTT_ConfigDownBuffer=
()</span></h4>
<p>Configure or add a down buffer by specifying its name, size and flags.
</p>
<h5><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Syntax">Syntax</span></h5>
<p><tt>int SEGGER_RTT_ConfigDownBuffer (unsigned BufferIndex, const char* s=
Name, char* pBuffer, int BufferSize, int Flags);</tt>
</p>
<table class=3D"seggertable">
<tbody><tr>
<th>Parameter</th>
<th>Meaning
</th></tr>
<tr>
<td><tt>BufferIndex</tt></td>
<td>Index of the buffer to configure.<br>Must be lower than SEGGER_RTT_MAX_=
NUM_DOWN_CHANNELS.
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><tt>sName</tt></td>
<td>Pointer to a 0-terminated string to be displayed as the name of the cha=
nnel.
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><tt>pBuffer</tt></td>
<td>Pointer to a buffer used by the channel.
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><tt>BufferSize</tt></td>
<td>Size of the buffer in Bytes.
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><tt>Flags</tt></td>
<td>Flags of the channel (blocking or non-blocking).<br>Flags[31:24]: Used =
for validity check, must be zero.<br>Flags[23:2]: Reserved for future use.<=
br>Flags[1:0]: RTT operating mode.
</td></tr></tbody></table>
<h5><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Return_value">Return value</span></h5=
>
<table class=3D"seggertable">
<tbody><tr>
<th>Value</th>
<th>Meaning
</th></tr>
<tr>
<td>&gt;=3D 0</td>
<td>O.K.
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td>&lt; 0</td>
<td>Error
</td></tr></tbody></table>
<h5><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Example">Example</span></h5>
<div class=3D"mw-highlight mw-highlight-lang-c mw-content-ltr" dir=3D"ltr">=
<pre><span></span><span class=3D"c1">//</span>
<span class=3D"c1">// Configure down buffer 1</span>
<span class=3D"c1">//</span>
<span class=3D"n">SEGGER_RTT_ConfigDownBuffer</span><span class=3D"p">(</sp=
an><span class=3D"mi">1</span><span class=3D"p">,</span><span class=3D"w"> =
</span><span class=3D"s">"DataIn"</span><span class=3D"p">,</span><span cla=
ss=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"o">&amp;</span><span class=3D"n">abDataIn</=
span><span class=3D"p">[</span><span class=3D"mi">0</span><span class=3D"p"=
>],</span><span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"k">sizeof</span><span cl=
ass=3D"p">(</span><span class=3D"n">abDataIn</span><span class=3D"p">),</sp=
an><span class=3D"w"></span>
<span class=3D"w">                             </span><span class=3D"n">SEG=
GER_RTT_MODE_NO_BLOCK_SKIP</span><span class=3D"p">);</span><span class=3D"=
w"></span>
</pre></div>
<h5><span class=3D"mw-headline" id=3D"Additional_information">Additional in=
formation</span></h5>
<p>Once a buffer is configured only the flags of the buffer should be chang=
ed.
</p>
<h4><span id=3D"SEGGER_RTT_ConfigUpBuffer.28.29"></span><span class=3D"mw-h=
eadline" id=3D"SEGGER_RTT_ConfigUpBuffer()">SEGGER_RTT_ConfigUpBuffer()</sp=
an></h4>
