NUM_UP_CHANNELS.
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td>sName</td>
<td>Pointer to a 0-terminated string to be displayed as the name of the cha=
nnel.
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td>pBuffer</td>
<td>Pointer to a buffer used by the channel.
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td>BufferSize</td>
