pan><span class=3D"o">=3D</span><span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"n"=
>SEGGER_RTT_WaitKey</span><span class=3D"p">();</span><span class=3D"w"></s=
pan>
<span class=3D"p">}</span><span class=3D"w"> </span><span class=3D"k">while=
